            <dd>
              An Ishgardian delicacy, the pickorpokkur are usually enjoyed for their fresh crunch.
              This pickorpokkur seems to have not only survived the pickling process, but grown stronger as a result.
            </dd>
            <dt><%= t('tooltip') %></dt>
            <dd>As you can see, I seem to have found myself in a pickle, and by pickle I mean the ground...<br>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Hildibrand</dd>
            <div class="d-block d-sm-none">
              <%= safe_image_tag("mounts/large/pickorpokkur.png", class: 'image-large') %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
